{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>明明想在学校中请一些同学一起做一项问卷调查，为了实验的客观性，他先用计算机生成了N个1到1000之间的随机整数（N≤100），对于其中重复的数字，只保留一个，把其余相同的数去掉，不同的数对应着不同的学生的学号。然后再把这些数从小到大排序，按照排好的顺序去找同学做调查。请你协助明明完成“去重”与“排序”的工作。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"明明的随机数 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>也是2行，第1行为1个正整数M，表示不相同的随机数的个数。第2行为M个用空格隔开的正整数，为从小到大排好序的不相同的随机数。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>有2行，第1行为1个正整数，表示所生成的随机数的个数：N；<p><p>第2行有N个用空格隔开的正整数，为所产生的随机数。<p>","examples":"<input>10\n20 40 32 67 40 20 89 300 400 15\n\n</input><output>8\n15 20 32 40 67 89 300 400\n\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1184","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}